trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle"></xref> objects in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.

trans-unit.source: The SubMenuStyleCollection class is used to store and manage a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle> objects in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: A classe de SubMenuStyleCollection é utilizada para armazenar e gerir uma coleção de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>objetos num <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>controlo.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control uses the SubMenuStyleCollection class as the underlying data type of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>controlo utiliza a classe de SubMenuStyleCollection como o tipo de dados subjacente a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> property provides additional style choices in addition to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuStyle%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DynamicMenuStyle%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>propriedade fornece opções de estilo adicionais para além de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuStyle%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DynamicMenuStyle%2A>Propriedades.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DynamicMenuStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>

trans-unit.source: The first style in the SubMenuStyleCollection collection corresponds to the submenu style for the first level of the menu.
trans-unit.target: O estilo primeiro na coleção SubMenuStyleCollection corresponde ao estilo do submenu para o primeiro nível do menu.

trans-unit.source: The second style in the collection corresponds to the submenu style for the second level of the menu, and so on.
trans-unit.target: O estilo do segundo na coleção corresponde ao estilo do submenu para o segundo nível de menu e assim sucessivamente.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> property is most often used to generate a navigation menu, like a Web site map, where menu items at a certain level should have the same appearance, regardless of whether they have submenus.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>propriedade frequentemente é utilizada para gerar um menu de navegação, como um mapa de Web site, onde os itens de menu num determinado nível devem ter o mesmo aspeto, independentemente se tiverem os submenus.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>
